### Все посты
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts

### Создать (id=0)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "content": "Hello, Netology!"
}

### Получить по id
GET    http://localhost:8080/servlets/api/posts
POST   http://localhost:8080/servlets/api/posts
GET    http://localhost:8080/servlets/api/posts/1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/servlets/api/posts/1

### Обновить существующий (id != 0)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "content": "Updated content"
}

### Удалить
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1